Interface TileServer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BingMapsTileServer, FileTileServer, GoogleMapsTileServer, OSMTileServer, PostGISRasterTileServer, WCSTileServer, WMSTileServer, WMTSTileServer

    public interface TileServer
